  "author_association": "NONE",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "What is the idea behind making the the `owner` private in https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/master/contracts/access/Ownable.sol#L19?\r\n\r\nIn most cases the owner should be set by the overwriting contract, rather than the `msg.sender` as in the internal constructor.\r\n\r\nWhat is the thinking behind this choice?\r\n",
